            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-04-19</p>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed watch-folder cases where real arrivals could be
skipped as too old.</strong> Files moved in by automation tools are now
recognized more consistently.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed reconciliation edge cases during monitor stop and
restart cycles.</strong> Deferred scans and replay behavior now converge
more reliably.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed startup database adoption edge cases across app
versions.</strong> Launch-time state is less likely to fail when older
store paths are present.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed currency consistency gaps between checkout and paywall
flows.</strong> Pricing and billing context now stay aligned more
reliably.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
